notes
We will make an optical campaign using  FPI, aurora imager, aurora cameras, proton imagers
and 4-wavelength photometer with the EISCAT UHF radar (CP-1, arc1 or beata,
tristatic measurements).
Clear sky and higher geomagnetic activity are desired.

So, we will run this SP for 2 nights out of 3 night requested.
